WEBVTT

00:07.842 --> 00:11.585
Johnny, those go to gen pop,
these go on the trucks.

00:11.762 --> 00:13.263
Don't get caught, you hear?

00:13.431 --> 00:16.764
Sneaky fucks.
They're putting hep V in the blood supply.

00:16.934 --> 00:19.676
-What's that? What's hep V?
-|t's this.

00:22.523 --> 00:24.434
I'm sorry, Nora.

00:24.609 --> 00:28.602
Go back in, find Pam,
tell her not to drink the Tru Blood.

00:28.779 --> 00:30.394
Okay.

00:33.201 --> 00:34.532
I'll come back for you.

00:34.702 --> 00:37.068
-But just remem--
-I got it. Go.

00:50.343 --> 00:52.800
-What the hell?
-Heh-heh-heh.

00:56.182 --> 00:57.547
