01:06.484 --> 01:08.270
AUTOMATED VOICE: Lockdown.
Secure the premises.

01:08.444 --> 01:10.935
[MEN YELLING INDISTINCTLY]

01:11.113 --> 01:12.899
Morris, what's going on?

01:13.074 --> 01:14.405
Northman escaped.

01:14.575 --> 01:16.361
Goddamn it!
That tricky motherfucker!

01:16.535 --> 01:19.572
-Stackhouse, you get to gen pop.
-Yes, sir.

01:21.415 --> 01:22.746
Gen pop.

01:29.215 --> 01:30.250
That's everything.

01:34.428 --> 01:35.929
GUARD:
Hey! Hey, hey, hold on a minute.

01:36.097 --> 01:38.213
DRIVER: What?
GUARD: Gotta do a security check.

01:38.724 --> 01:40.339
Reports of vampires in the area.

01:40.518 --> 01:42.383
DRIVER: I'm on a schedule, though.
Hurry it up.

01:42.561 --> 01:44.062
GUARD:
Yeah, I know.

01:52.655 --> 01:54.316
Oh, shit.

01:56.659 --> 01:57.944
All set!

03:57.488 --> 03:58.853
Let's go!

03:59.073 --> 04:00.813
[ALARM BLARING]

04:09.333 --> 04:11.824
I thought that
you would be chained up.

04:12.002 --> 04:14.664
PAM: l was, but I got a fan
in the Psych Department.

04:14.839 --> 04:17.125
What are you doing here?

04:17.633 --> 04:19.169
Eric sent me to help you.

04:19.343 --> 04:21.459
Eric sent you?

04:21.637 --> 04:23.138
-To help me?
-Yes, he did.

04:23.305 --> 04:25.011
And if you want me
to save your ass...

04:25.182 --> 04:27.969
...you might wanna tone it down
with the attitude.

04:29.311 --> 04:30.721
I'm all ears.

04:30.896 --> 04:34.138
They're gonna start giving us Tru Blood,
but you cannot drink it.

04:35.443 --> 04:37.650
There's hep V in it.

04:38.237 --> 04:40.899
-What the hell is that?
-I don't know, but it is not good.

04:41.073 --> 04:42.108
Nora has it.

04:45.161 --> 04:46.401
Who else knows?

04:47.580 --> 04:50.697
-lt's just you and me.
-Good, keep it that way.

04:52.126 --> 04:54.833
Tell Tara and Jessica,
but fuck everyone else.

04:55.004 --> 04:57.916
Okay, I know that being charitable
isn't real vampire-like...

04:58.090 --> 05:01.173
...but don't we want
to save our kind?

05:01.343 --> 05:03.550
If every vampire stops feeding...

05:03.721 --> 05:05.882
...those pervy fucks
will know we're onto them.

05:06.056 --> 05:09.344
Our only chance of fixing this shit show
is if they don't suspect us.

05:09.518 --> 05:11.383
Of course.

05:13.022 --> 05:14.603
How are they treating you in here?

05:15.357 --> 05:17.814
Like a princess. Can't you tell?

05:18.360 --> 05:19.566
I got this.

05:19.737 --> 05:21.819
I can sneak you into gen pop.

05:22.198 --> 05:25.611
Severed arm. Not bad.

05:25.784 --> 05:26.910
But too obvious.

05:27.077 --> 05:29.284
No, just get yourself back in there.

05:29.455 --> 05:31.286
I'll see you soon enough.

05:34.960 --> 05:36.951
[ALARM BLARING]

05:40.216 --> 05:42.628
[INDISTINCT CHATTERING]

06:00.986 --> 06:02.146
[NORA MOANING]

06:07.451 --> 06:09.533
ERIC:
I don't know what you are.

06:09.703 --> 06:12.319
All I know is I saw Sookie stake you
and you survived.

06:13.290 --> 06:16.953
But if you are God...

06:20.422 --> 06:21.628
...please heal her for me.

06:28.681 --> 06:30.922
I feel hot.

06:31.100 --> 06:32.840
How is that possible?

06:38.148 --> 06:39.228
Give her your blood.

06:39.400 --> 06:42.107
No, no, please.
It's Lilith's blood.

06:42.278 --> 06:43.814
-I won't drink.
-Sister, please.

06:43.988 --> 06:45.478
-No, brother.
-Sister, you have to--

06:45.656 --> 06:47.066
I'd rather die
than have Lilith's blood.

06:47.241 --> 06:49.072
You can't blame her.
You saw what the blood did to us.

06:49.243 --> 06:52.656
-And I don't care about that. Just do it.
-I can't do it, Eric.

06:52.997 --> 06:56.034
-Do it.
-This is her dying wish.

06:56.917 --> 06:58.703
We have to honor it.

07:04.842 --> 07:06.332
Leave.

07:08.679 --> 07:09.714
Leave us!

07:18.230 --> 07:20.471
WOMAN [OVER SPEAKER]:
Welcome back to e/ocution classes...

07:20.649 --> 07:22.731
...for spreading the Gospel.
Chapter Three.

07:22.901 --> 07:26.359
Drop one octave and repeat,
"God is good. "

07:26.530 --> 07:29.021
God is good.

07:29.575 --> 07:31.486
"God is our savior. "

07:33.078 --> 07:36.241
God is....

07:40.002 --> 07:41.742
Why are there no guards?

07:41.920 --> 07:45.412
Remember to be strong,
yet not assertive.

07:45.591 --> 07:47.673
Truman?

07:55.476 --> 07:57.216
[WHISPERS]
Truman....

08:10.449 --> 08:12.155
Oh, no.

08:13.202 --> 08:14.612
What did they do to you?

08:14.828 --> 08:16.819
[SOBBING]

08:25.714 --> 08:27.579
Oh, Truman Burrell.

08:27.758 --> 08:30.545
Oh, God.

08:32.721 --> 08:36.930
You were a decent, decent man...

08:37.101 --> 08:40.969
...and your commitment
to this cause was whole...

08:41.480 --> 08:43.971
...and it was pure.

08:50.781 --> 08:54.694
But these monsters prey on the pure.

08:58.539 --> 09:02.623
Know that your death was not in vain...

09:03.377 --> 09:08.212
...for it will galvanize the forces
against this evil we fight.

09:11.677 --> 09:13.963
This was part of God's plan.

09:18.183 --> 09:24.600
And God is good.

09:32.448 --> 09:34.439
[FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING]

09:35.075 --> 09:37.817
[COUGHS THEN GRUNTS]

09:37.995 --> 09:40.156
Thank you for coming so quickly, senator.

09:40.330 --> 09:42.161
What in the hell happened?

09:42.541 --> 09:45.999
-I think it's pretty clear.
-Well, how'd they get to him?

09:46.170 --> 09:48.411
There were more men
on this place than Fort Knox.

09:48.589 --> 09:51.501
Are you really still surprised
by what they're capable of?

09:51.842 --> 09:54.879
Well, not surprised, just disappointed.

09:55.053 --> 09:58.181
-I thought we were making progress.
-We are.

09:58.348 --> 10:01.055
That is the biblical irony in all this.

10:01.977 --> 10:04.810
The things we are learning every day...

10:04.980 --> 10:06.936
...they are just shy of miracles.

10:07.900 --> 10:11.518
We are this close...

10:11.695 --> 10:14.607
...to bringing Truman's vision to light.

10:14.782 --> 10:17.194
I don't see that happening now...

10:17.367 --> 10:19.574
...not with this lieutenant governor
sitting in his seat.

10:19.745 --> 10:21.656
SARAH:
Oh, no.

10:21.830 --> 10:25.493
I am not letting that RINO
with his folksy bullshit...

10:25.667 --> 10:27.874
...step one foot near this office.

10:28.045 --> 10:30.536
That's why I brought you here,
to help me.

10:31.256 --> 10:33.463
No one can know Truman's gone.

10:34.426 --> 10:36.291
Sarah...

10:36.470 --> 10:38.711
...how do you cover up
something like this?

10:39.097 --> 10:40.712
I know you know fixers...

10:41.391 --> 10:46.101
...professionals you keep on retainer
to cover up your seedy lifestyle.

10:47.314 --> 10:48.599
Call them.

10:49.399 --> 10:54.109
Have them move the late,
great governor's body away...

10:54.279 --> 10:55.735
...and dispose of it.

10:55.906 --> 10:57.897
And I don't wanna know how...

10:58.075 --> 11:00.566
...but I do hear acid is effective.

11:06.083 --> 11:07.619
Then?

11:07.793 --> 11:11.251
We release a statement
saying the compound was attacked...

11:11.421 --> 11:14.254
...but Truman escaped unharmed
and is continuing to govern...

11:14.424 --> 11:16.585
...from an undisclosed location.

11:17.261 --> 11:19.126
We will wipe this place down...

11:19.304 --> 11:23.138
...and then you will cover for him
in legislature.

11:24.935 --> 11:27.893
And I will be his presence
at the facility...

11:28.063 --> 11:30.224
...and on all matters vampire.

11:30.399 --> 11:32.230
How long you expect us
to pull this off?

11:32.401 --> 11:35.063
Tainted Tru Blood will be
on grocery shelves any day now.

11:35.237 --> 11:37.944
Hep V will spread like wildfire.

11:38.115 --> 11:40.276
We're not talking long.

11:42.536 --> 11:43.742
Make the call.

11:44.413 --> 11:45.949
Of course, David.

11:47.749 --> 11:50.126
When I hired you
to consult on my last campaign...

11:50.294 --> 11:53.957
...I knew there was something there,
but this, Sarah...

11:54.131 --> 11:55.962
...this is quite impressive.

11:56.133 --> 11:58.294
Just you wait, senator.

11:58.802 --> 12:01.134
When God's message is this clear...

12:01.305 --> 12:04.638
...I am a truly unstoppable woman.

12:23.619 --> 12:24.654
[CLEARS THROAT]

12:24.828 --> 12:29.197
-Well, this is a first.
-Hmm?

12:29.374 --> 12:33.492
Waking up with a man
in broad daylight.

12:34.963 --> 12:37.545
You just wrote our wedding vows.

12:37.716 --> 12:39.297
Right.

12:39.468 --> 12:41.459
