in the cemetery. I have to go to her.

14:02.134 --> 14:04.295
I'll come back for you
just as soon as I can.

14:06.847 --> 14:09.259
-How do I get out of here?
-Use your light.

14:09.641 --> 14:11.347
You've had my blood. It'll work.

14:22.195 --> 14:23.810
