14:32.039 --> 14:33.654
What happened?

14:33.832 --> 14:35.493
They shot him.

14:35.667 --> 14:37.623
-Who?
-I don't know.

14:37.794 --> 14:40.627
All I know is that one minute...

14:40.797 --> 14:42.788
...he was struggling with his demons...

14:42.966 --> 14:45.002
...and they were getting
the better of him...

14:45.177 --> 14:47.793
...so I called this vampire friend
of Holly's...

14:47.971 --> 14:50.428
...and he glamored away
all the bad stuff...

14:50.599 --> 14:53.011
...and then he was doing much better.

14:53.185 --> 14:56.018
I mean, he was the old Terry...

14:56.188 --> 14:59.680
...and I got a glimmer
of what it was gonna be like...

14:59.858 --> 15:03.646
...Iife with him happy.

15:03.820 --> 15:05.776
And it was....

15:05.947 --> 15:09.906
Oh, it was the best feeling
I'd ever had.

15:11.286 --> 15:14.699
Oh, my God!
What am I gonna do, Sookie?

15:14.873 --> 15:16.864
