15:17.042 --> 15:18.907
Listen to me, Arlene.

15:19.086 --> 15:20.246
You gotta tell your kids.

15:20.420 --> 15:23.287
They need to know
what happened to their daddy.

15:24.299 --> 15:28.417
I don't know if I can say the words.

15:28.595 --> 15:30.096
Look at me.

15:30.263 --> 15:33.130
You're one of the strongest
people I know.

15:33.517 --> 15:35.883
I don't know why you've been tested
the way you have...

15:36.061 --> 15:37.972
...but you always get through...

15:38.480 --> 15:41.096
...and I'm gonna be there
to make sure that you do...

15:41.274 --> 15:47.235
...just like you're gonna be there
for Coby, Lisa and Mikey, all right?

15:48.573 --> 15:50.529
Yeah, okay.

15:55.622 --> 15:57.613
