18:21.977 --> 18:24.389
You and I's got an errand to run.

18:26.189 --> 18:29.647
Maybe this time
it'll be your ass that gets kicked.

18:32.654 --> 18:34.019
Hamby.

18:37.284 --> 18:39.240
Oh, great.

18:41.830 --> 18:43.536
GUARD:
In here.

18:55.135 --> 18:57.126
Jason.

18:57.304 --> 18:58.840
What are you doing here?

19:00.682 --> 19:03.048
I came to--

19:05.270 --> 19:06.976
Come here.

19:10.608 --> 19:11.734
I came to help you.

19:11.901 --> 19:14.028
