-What?

19:23.413 --> 19:25.199
I'm gonna get you out of here...

19:25.373 --> 19:26.954
...and I ain't gonna let you down.

19:27.125 --> 19:28.535
You don't have to do that.

19:28.960 --> 19:30.825
Yeah, I do.

19:31.004 --> 19:33.495
Jess, my thoughts ain't always so clear...

19:33.673 --> 19:36.915
...but my heart,
it ain't never been so clear...

19:37.093 --> 19:38.958
...that I wanna do right by you.

19:39.137 --> 19:40.547
No.

19:41.514 --> 19:43.891
I mean, you don't have
to get me out of here.

19:44.434 --> 19:47.642
You don't have that
"Stockholders' syndrome," do you?

19:47.812 --> 19:50.019
No, I just--

19:50.190 --> 19:52.977
I just sort of know
how it's gonna work out...

19:54.944 --> 19:57.526
-...and I'm okay with it.
-There is nothing okay...

19:57.697 --> 20:00.029
...with the shit that's been
going on in here.

20:07.332 --> 20:10.415
I was there yesterday...

20:12.587 --> 20:16.296
...when they tried to get
the vampire to have sex with you.

20:17.634 --> 20:20.546
It made me sick
to watch you go through that.

20:22.389 --> 20:24.880
You will never, never suffer again.

20:26.726 --> 20:29.763
Jason, you cannot stop...

20:29.938 --> 20:31.724
...bad things from happening to me.

20:31.898 --> 20:34.139
We don't live in that kind of world.

20:37.320 --> 20:39.356
I'm sorry.

20:39.531 --> 20:42.443
All you can do is go on being...

20:42.617 --> 20:46.735
-...the sweet, wonderful man that you are.
-Hmm.

20:49.624 --> 20:53.082
But if you really wanna do right by me...

20:53.920 --> 20:57.128
-...there's something I could use your help with.
-Tell me what it is.

20:58.550 --> 21:00.040
That vampire...

21:00.218 --> 21:01.833
...the one who wouldn't--

21:02.679 --> 21:05.512
I'd really like to thank him for that.

21:05.682 --> 21:07.968
Like, face-to-face.

21:09.894 --> 21:11.475
Oh.

21:16.276 --> 21:17.391
I'll go get him for you.

21:23.867 --> 21:27.234
[DOOR OPENS THEN CLOSES]

22:37.899 --> 22:39.890
