22:57.252 --> 23:00.494
I'll be outside if you have any questions.

23:17.397 --> 23:19.262
Life insurance?

23:22.610 --> 23:24.521
This was issued just three days ago.

23:27.323 --> 23:28.483
He knew it was coming.

23:29.367 --> 23:33.576
Shit, he had the whole
motherfucking thing planned.

23:33.746 --> 23:37.113
And pretty well.
This is a lot of money.

23:40.169 --> 23:41.500
How can you do it?

23:42.589 --> 23:45.422
You do it when you believe
it's the best thing for everybody.

23:46.050 --> 23:49.167
When is leaving your family behind
ever the best thing?

23:50.847 --> 23:52.678
I don't know, Sook.

23:52.849 --> 23:54.805
I don't know.

23:58.813 --> 24:00.804
[UPBEAT MUSIC
PLAYING OVER CAR STEREO]

24:12.744 --> 24:14.280
[MUSIC STOPS]

24:14.454 --> 24:16.536
You wanna stay for a beer,
maybe a couple?

24:16.706 --> 24:19.288
Thanks, but I gotta get back.

24:21.753 --> 24:25.712
The problem I have
is I've fucked up so many times...

24:25.882 --> 24:29.249
...ain't nothing I can say
that's gonna mean that much to you.

24:29.886 --> 24:32.047
That's my cross to bear.

24:39.270 --> 24:40.680
You see that fresh grass...

24:40.855 --> 24:43.312
...growing over there on that little hillside?

24:43.816 --> 24:45.397
That's Old Mrs. Reed's land.

24:45.568 --> 24:47.274
Yeah, except not no more.

24:47.445 --> 24:49.561
She met a fella
and moved to North Dakota.

24:50.740 --> 24:51.775
So?

24:51.949 --> 24:54.531
