JASON:
Hey.

46:24.157 --> 46:25.693
Back off, bitches.

46:25.867 --> 46:28.654
VIOLET:
Ladies, please.

46:30.163 --> 46:32.028
He's mine.

46:34.417 --> 46:35.918
JASON:
Hmm.

46:52.435 --> 46:53.811
ALCIDE:
It's done.

46:55.730 --> 46:57.641
Sam Merlotte and the girl are dead.

46:58.108 --> 46:59.518
MAN 1: Yeah.
WOMAN: All right.

46:59.693 --> 47:02.856
-What about the pup?
-I gave Emma to Martha.

47:03.029 --> 47:05.020
It was the right thing to do.

47:05.198 --> 47:08.486
They'll stay away
and we'll lose this heat on us...

47:08.994 --> 47:11.986
...which Should make you happy.

47:12.163 --> 47:13.744
It does.

47:15.542 --> 47:18.158
Of course I'd be a lot happier...

47:18.336 --> 47:21.703
...if you weren't lying through
your motherfucking teeth right now.

47:21.881 --> 47:22.916
-What?
MAN 2: That's right.

47:23.091 --> 47:26.208
Be a doll and bring the ladies out,
will you, Tiffany?

47:28.638 --> 47:30.629
[MUFFLED WHIMPERING]

47:37.022 --> 47:38.057
Look who I found...

47:39.983 --> 47:42.269
...very much alive.

47:42.444 --> 47:44.025
MAN 3:
Motherfucking liar.

47:44.195 --> 47:46.777
MAN 4: Fucking liar!
MAN 5: Bullshit.

47:48.116 --> 47:49.606
Godric?

47:55.290 --> 47:57.201
Godric, whatever magic you possess...

47:57.375 --> 47:59.957
...can you use it now, please?

48:08.428 --> 48:11.386
I beg of you, Godric, please, can you...

48:11.556 --> 48:13.968
...just give her
one more chance like you--?

48:14.142 --> 48:15.803
Like you've done before?

48:18.104 --> 48:20.811
NORA:
It was you who gave it to me.

48:22.275 --> 48:26.609
You. You who saw something in me...

48:26.780 --> 48:28.736
...found me.

48:30.408 --> 48:32.524
Do you remember?

48:35.205 --> 48:37.161
Of course I remember it.

48:42.295 --> 48:43.831
Your Majesty.

48:45.215 --> 48:46.250
You look pale.

48:47.675 --> 48:49.131
Paler than usual.

48:49.302 --> 48:53.341
The plague,
it has made food scarce...

48:53.807 --> 48:55.672
...as you can imagine.

48:55.850 --> 48:57.386
Indeed.

49:06.986 --> 49:10.444
This outbreak grieves me greatly also.
Have you heard Of the Lady Gainesborough?

49:10.615 --> 49:12.981
I have heard her name...

49:13.159 --> 49:16.367
...in reference to an affection...

49:16.538 --> 49:18.153
...you two share, sire.

49:18.790 --> 49:20.997
Then you've heard correctly.

49:22.669 --> 49:26.412
She's a woman of strong will,
and as such, She's currently in London...

49:26.589 --> 49:29.877
...tending to the poor bastards
dying of the pestilence.

49:30.051 --> 49:32.793
-Oh, how commendable.
-It's bloody madness.

49:32.971 --> 49:34.552
The woman has a death wish...

49:34.722 --> 49:36.804
...and I would let her die
of her impudence...

49:36.975 --> 49:40.092
...if I didn't find her presence
in my bedchamber such a necessity.

49:40.270 --> 49:42.261
I see.

49:42.438 --> 49:44.690
I'm not sure you do.

49:45.567 --> 49:47.853
Her insubordination makes for bed sport...

49:48.027 --> 49:51.235
...the likes of which I have never known.

49:51.739 --> 49:54.867
She has a great value to you.

49:55.743 --> 49:57.074
Which is why I need you...

49:57.245 --> 50:00.487
...to promptly remove her
from her vile Situation.

50:00.665 --> 50:02.075
And upon her return...

50:03.293 --> 50:07.662
...I shall see that you are fed
exceedingly well.

50:09.424 --> 50:10.755
Hmm.

50:12.969 --> 50:14.175
Your Majesty.

50:22.020 --> 50:23.851
[MAN 1 GRUNTS]

50:24.480 --> 50:26.732
MAN 2:
Are there any upstairs?

50:27.775 --> 50:30.266
MAN 1: Yeah.
MAN 2: Easy.

50:30.945 --> 50:32.151
[WOMEN CRYING]

50:32.322 --> 50:34.062
WOMAN:
No!

50:34.282 --> 50:36.273
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

51:01.976 --> 51:06.686
Are you mad?
Can't you see that we're quarantined?

51:06.856 --> 51:08.938
I'm looking for Lady Gainesborough.

51:09.734 --> 51:13.647
You're too late.
The pustules have formed.

51:13.947 --> 51:15.437
Show me to her.

51:16.157 --> 51:18.489
On your own head be it.

51:26.668 --> 51:28.909
[MAN SPEAKS |N FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

51:31.714 --> 51:35.127
Milady, I'm Eric Northman...

51:35.301 --> 51:37.007
...a friend of the king's.

51:38.221 --> 51:40.212
[WOMEN SCREAMING |N DISTANCE]

51:48.314 --> 51:50.225
I will take you
somewhere more peaceful.

51:50.400 --> 51:52.015
No.

51:53.528 --> 51:55.519
I am not long.

51:55.947 --> 51:59.485
The king insists you rest
in better conditions.

51:59.659 --> 52:02.401
I do not want to die in his presence.

52:02.787 --> 52:06.780
-What of your house in Surrey?
-His house in Surrey.

52:06.958 --> 52:08.823
No.

52:10.545 --> 52:12.661
My death shall be my own.

52:17.302 --> 52:18.633
[CHUCKLES]

52:23.725 --> 52:26.011
He called you stubborn...

52:28.313 --> 52:31.976
...but he has that confused
with courage it would seem.

52:37.864 --> 52:39.695
How are you so brave?

52:42.035 --> 52:44.321
lam...

52:45.330 --> 52:46.991
...immune.

52:48.541 --> 52:50.782
You have the look
of destiny about you.

52:58.551 --> 53:00.462
Let me take you to my father.

53:00.845 --> 53:02.676
He can heal you.

53:02.847 --> 53:04.929
Can he fully, though?

53:08.269 --> 53:10.760
I would not want to live like this.

53:10.938 --> 53:13.429
You will live fully...

53:13.608 --> 53:15.473
...and forever.

53:16.694 --> 53:17.774
I promise.

53:21.908 --> 53:25.071
[NORA GASPING]

53:28.247 --> 53:30.158
And so we end as we began.

53:31.793 --> 53:35.331
Only this time,
there is no Godric to heal me.

53:36.964 --> 53:39.250
Only you to comfort me.

53:39.759 --> 53:41.795
Who's gonna comfort me
for centuries to come?

53:41.969 --> 53:45.132
Pamela and Willa.

53:45.306 --> 53:46.967
You saw in them
what you saw in me.

53:47.141 --> 53:49.678
Yeah, but you will never be replaced.

53:49.852 --> 53:52.104
Let them walk beside you.

53:52.271 --> 53:53.977
They want to.

53:56.484 --> 53:58.270
Just as I did.

53:59.570 --> 54:03.404
-I promised you forever.
-Brother, listen.

54:04.158 --> 54:07.116
I only ever asked to live fully.

54:08.079 --> 54:09.660
And you gave me that.

54:16.337 --> 54:17.372
[G RU NTS]

54:17.547 --> 54:20.289
No. NO, no, no.
Don't....

54:21.717 --> 54:23.173
Please don't-- Don't leave me.

54:23.344 --> 54:24.800
Don't leave me. Don't....

54:27.181 --> 54:28.591
Nora, don't leave me.

54:28.766 --> 54:30.506
Please. . ..

54:31.436 --> 54:33.176
[ERIC SOBBING]

54:33.396 --> 54:35.478
Please don't leave me.

54:35.648 --> 54:37.809
Please don't leave me!

54:38.067 --> 54:40.058
[SCREAMS]
